CustomField.description: GeoResults assigned number indicating the relative position for this business location north or south from the equator. Paired with the longitude for this business location, the coordinates can be used to determine relative distances to network elements, assignments to standard geographic areas and assignments to standard telecommunications areas for this business. Latitude is given in degrees to six decimal places.
